### Home
GET http://localhost:8080/api/catalog/home?limit=24

### Products list
GET http://localhost:8080/api/catalog/products?category=&q=&min=&max=&attrs=color:red,size:M&sort=price,asc&page=1

### Product detail
GET http://localhost:8080/api/catalog/products/sample-slug

### Store detail
GET http://localhost:8080/api/catalog/stores/sample-store

### Seller - My Store
GET http://localhost:8080/api/catalog/my/store
X-User-Roles: SELLER

### Seller - Create Product
POST http://localhost:8080/api/catalog/products
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Roles: SELLER

{
  "name": "Sample Product",
  "price": 199.90,
  "currency": "TRY",
  "stock": 10,
  "categoryId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
  "attrs": {
    "color": "red",
    "size": "M"
  }
}

### Seller - Presigned URLs
POST http://localhost:8080/api/catalog/products/{{productId}}/images/presign
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Roles: SELLER

{
  "count": 3
}

### Admin - Approve Store
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/catalog/stores/{{storeId}}/approve
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Roles: ADMIN

{
  "isApproved": true
}

### Admin - Set Product Active
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/catalog/products/{{productId}}/active
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Roles: ADMIN

{
  "isActive": false
}
